metadata.title: Vaultz Locking Makeup Artist Case, Black White Stripe (VZ03755)
features: Perfect for a large makeup collection
Built-in 14 brush holder in lid with cover; Customize space with 5 adjustable dividers
Convenient handle for easy carrying; Sturdy key lock
Removable, divided, upper tray for simple access to lower compartment
Hard-sided construction prevents items from being crushed
description: At Vaultz, "If it's Important to You, Lock It Up." The Vaultz Makeup Artist Case allows you to lock your personal and private items up in style. This durable and chic box is ideal for carrying makeup and other cosmetics on the go. The reliable key lock provides security, and the sturdy construction features steel corners, aluminum reinforcement, and a convenient handle for easy carrying. This makeup case features a built-in 14 brush holder in lid, a removable, divided, upper tray for simple access to lower compartment and 5 adjustable dividers to customize the space. This is a makeup case that you are sure to love. Black White Stripe.
